snippet.title: Fashion Channel
snippet.description: Fashion Channel brings you the best videos and the most exclusive moments of the international runway since 1982 until now, the most representative fashion weeks of the world. Backstage secrets, insights on hair and make-up, curiosities from the fashion world, celebrities, photoshoots, clips of designers and models, red carpets and gossip, parties, the best fashion shows of all the top designers.
